headline.main: NEW-JERSEY.; Visit of the New-Haven Blues. Corner Stone.

docs.lead_paragraph: The New-Haven Blues, Capt. BRISTOL, arrived in the New-Haven boat yesterday morning, as previously announced, on their visit to Hoboken. The Highwood Guard, Capt. HATFIELD, of Hoboken, whose guests the Blues are, were at Peck-slip at 8 o'clock, and received the Blues with a military welcome.
